 <p class="dfe-c-body-s muted dfe-c-mb-2">No reporting periods are configured. Add periods in <a href="@Url.Action("WorkReporting", "ModernAdmin")" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state">Admin → Work reporting</a>.</p>
